1. Prepare proof of your old assets 


2. Contact the users who have registered BVW. At least 10 people (the original team members) register to download BVW and activate BID. 


3. Fill in the [Resurrection Plan] application form, and enter each period of [Resurrection Plan] training group, and conduct each period of [Resurrection Plan] special training, and officially join the [Resurrection Plan] directory after the training 


4. After joining the [Resurrection Plan] directory, submit the BVW payment address and asset certificate.

6. After completing the purchase of the BVW agreement, a redemption payment of USD 50,000 to USD 200,000 per person will be made according to the loss amount. When the user's total performance exceeds US $ 2 million, the instruction to enter the mining pool by 10% of the performance will automatically disappear)

How to activate the mining pool: \nAdd 10% daily results to the [Resurrection Plan] mining pool and activate the "[Resurrection Plan] Dream Startup bouns". \n(Each user\'s dream start-up fund does not exceed US $ 200,000. After reaching US $ 200,000, 10% of new performance will not flow into the [Resurrection Plan] mining pool)
\n\nNote: [Resurrection Plan] The user needs to meet the requirement to hold at least 200 BVW before the system will start to activate the inflow of mining pools.

[Resurrection Plan] The release of Dream Starter bouns will be linked to the daily increase of BVW. The daily percentage increase of BVW at 00:10 will be used as the percentage of the [Resurrection Plan] mining pool release. (Negative increase does not make any reward) That is, the percentage increase of BVW on that day = the percentage of BVW mining pool balance release on that day. \nExample: The user participated in the [Resurrection Plan], and today the entire team added 1 million new results, which will flow into the [Resurrection Plan] mining pool 100X10%= 100,000, today\'s BVW increase by 5%, and users can get 100,000X5% = 5,000 yuan [resurrection plan] dream start money. Users can start trading / cashing on the released dream at any time.

[Resurrection Plan] In order to prevent users from controlling the market, the system synchronization will start the hibernation system. The dormant system is only effective for the [Resurrection Plan] user system and is not valid for normal BVW economic mode users. \nDescription of the dormant system: Users participating in the [Resurrection Plan] users can enter the Resurrection Plan mining pool system by adding 10% of their new performance, and the maximum mining pool capacity is ≤200,000 USDT.

If the user \’s total performance on that day is the highest historical performance, a new performance of 10% will flow into the [Resurrection Plan] mining pool, and the percentage of the mining pool balance will be released according to the percentage increase of BVW on that day; \nIf the user \’s total performance on that day is ≤ the historical highest performance, he will enter a dormant state, and the [Resurrection Plan] mining pool will stop releasing; when the user total performance is > historical highest performance, the hibernation state will be automatically released, and work will be performed in accordance with the system instructions.
